## Compatibility note

This file is the source of truth. It is loaded by:

- **Cursor** automatically as a global rule (via `~/.cursor/rules/agent-autonomy.mdc` symlink → this file)
- **Claude Code** via `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (symlink → this file)

If you edit this file, both clients pick up the change on the next session start. Do not duplicate this content elsewhere; edit it here and let the symlinks distribute it.
